flowchart TD
    subgraph Segments
        S1[Finance Department<br/>department -eq 'Finance']
        S2[HR Department]
    end

    subgraph Policies["Directional Policies"]
        P1["Finance-HR Block Policy<br/>Assigned Segment: Finance Department<br/>Blocked Segment: HR Department<br/>Allow Moderation: False<br/>Status: Active"]
        P2["HR-Finance Block Policy<br/>Assigned Segment: HR Department<br/>Blocked Segment: Finance Department<br/>Status: Active"]
    end

    S1 -->|assigned to| P1
    S2 -->|blocked by| P1
    S2 -->|assigned to| P2
    S1 -->|blocked by| P2

    P1 --> AP[Policy Application Engine]
    P2 --> AP

    AP -->|computes| REL["InformationBarrierRelationship<br/>Finance user <-> HR user"]

    REL --> C1["Communication1To2 = False<br/>(Finance -> HR blocked)"]
    REL --> C2["Communication2To1 = False<br/>(HR -> Finance blocked)"]
    REL --> V1["Visibility1To2 = False"]
    REL --> V2["Visibility2To1 = False"]

    C1 --> TEAMS[Microsoft Teams<br/>enforces at send-time]
    C2 --> TEAMS
